data.description: Welcome to your new family home! This charming 3-bedroom ranch-style property offers spacious, inviting rooms in a tranquil location nestled in the heart of Tottenville. Here, you'll enjoy the perfect blend of serenity and convenience, with easy access to transportation, shopping, schools, and recreation. Every room in this home is generously sized, providing ample space for comfortable living. Whether you're relaxing in the living room, preparing meals in the kitchen, or enjoying a peaceful night's sleep in one of the three bedrooms, you'll have plenty of room to spread out. The eat-in kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, ceramic backsplash and flooring, along with a bay window that floods the space with natural light.Throughout the home, you'll find hardwood floors that not only add to the aesthetic appeal but also make for easy maintenance. Crown molding adds a touch of sophistication, enhancing the overall charm of the property.The property has seen some valuable updates, including a 10-year-old roof, window replacements, and screens in the screen room. Newer front and back doors, new hot water tank, and furnace, and a new washer and dryer.  Step outside from your screen room to discover an inviting in-ground pool with heater surrounded by concrete and stamped concretew walkways. It's the perfect setting for outdoor gatherings, BBQs, or simply basking in the sun. There's also a shed with electricity, and the attic offers convenient pull-down stairs for additional storage. Two car off- street parking is a breeze. This lovely one-family ranch offers endless possibilities for possible expansion should you decide to build up, you'll have the space and potential to create your dream home.Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming ranch your forever home.
